title: Missouri's Mysterious Disappearance -  VANISHED Springfield 3 | Mystery and Makeup Bailey Sarian
author: Bailey Sarian
comment: I love that Bailey needs to explain 90s stuff (old school phones/answering machines, pre-cell phone etiquette etc) cuz you know some peeps watching were born after that wonderful era 😂💯
The thing I love about Bailey is that she just has not changed like she's gone from a small channel to over 5 million subscribers and she's still the same beautiful person x
I think I’m more weirded out by Janelle showing up at someone’s house barefoot than I am weirded out by the broom.

A 'crank' call is where the caller tries to annoy, disturb or deceive the person answering, and a 'prank' call is intended to 'trick' someone, being less harmful and more intended as a joke. You're welcome...

My mom would have cleaned her friend’s house too. 1: she cleans when she’s stressed and 2: she would be like, “strangers are coming over, she wouldn’t want them to see her house like this, let’s just straighten up a bit”
Literally didn’t surprise me at all. Dumb but if it wasn’t an “obvious” crime scene they probably wouldn’t have thought twice at all.
